DarkMouse::

She felt hurt at DarkFate's words as she listened in through the 
wires.  She sighed, "Yeah, geinuss it often unnoticed. I think I'll 
have to submit a resume or something."
She thought back to how she nearly singal pawed set up Megatron's old 
cave base, hacked into the maximal data base, reconfigured a hundred 
weapons systems and brought one bot back from the dead. Well, cloned 
a bot successfully at least.  She shook her head," It's just not easy 
being a mouse around carnivores like these."
